---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL.replace(/\/$/, '');
---

<Base title="About — Nicholas Maassen">
  <section class="about">
    <h1>About</h1>

    <p>
      I'm a full-stack software engineer with 2.5 years at Avodah Software, building client-facing
      products across payments, healthcare, scheduling, messaging, and admin tools.
    </p>

    <p>
      I work close to the problem. Most of my recent projects involved figuring out what a client
      actually needed (not just what they asked for), prototyping in production, and hardening
      integrations after real users got their hands on them. I care about Core Web Vitals, vendor
      coordination, multi-tenant OAuth, and the quiet kind of architecture that holds up under
      real traffic.
    </p>

    <h2>Currently</h2>

    <p>
      Looking for full-time roles as a Product Engineer, Full-Stack Engineer, or Forward Deployed
      Engineer at companies that take engineering writing seriously and ship to real users every week.
      Especially interested in developer tools, AI-augmented workflows, and integration-heavy products.
    </p>

    <h2>Tools I use daily</h2>

    <p>
      TypeScript, React, Node.js, PostgreSQL, Cloudflare Workers, Fly.io, Stripe Connect,
      Microsoft Graph, Clerk, Sentry. Claude Code and Codex with custom skills for output-driven
      prompts, multi-agent planning, and pre-review antipattern scans.
    </p>

    <h2>Reach me</h2>

    <ul class="contact-list">
      <li><a href="mailto:nicholasfmaassen@gmail.com">nicholasfmaassen@gmail.com</a></li>
      <li><a href="https://github.com/NMaass">github.com/NMaass</a></li>
      <li><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/nicholas-maassen-63ab53187/">LinkedIn</a></li>
      <li><a href={`${base}/resume.pdf`}>Resume (PDF)</a></li>
    </ul>
  </section>
</Base>

<style>
  .about {
    max-width: var(--max-width-prose);
    padding: var(--space-2xl) 0;
  }

  .about h1 {
    font-size: var(--text-4xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .about h2 {
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    margin-top: var(--space-2xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  }

  .about p {
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .contact-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .contact-list li {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }
</style>
